name: Mystical Creatures by Vikky. Strong in Spirit

metadata.name: Adena
metadata.description:
Adena. The phoenix bird. One of the most beautiful mystical creatures, symbolizing the will to live, the power of faith and soul. 
Adena is able to easily overcome all the hardships of life. The light of her soul illuminates her path. Adena is not afraid to make mistakes, because she knows that everything can be fixed.
Helps everyone to find harmony of soul and body.
